	    <h2 id="epilogue">Epilogue</h2>

	    <p>The people of the Karoo are asking the SKA International Partners States and the SKA Non-Partner States to take a close look at the SKA SA project which they are financing. Please consider the inhabitants of the Northern Cape and Africa now and in the future. The people of the Karoo need to be protected and future generations, including the unborn, need to be protected. The natural environment on which we depend must be protected from exploitation, destruction and from ecocide.</p>	      
	      
